  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for git-bug",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for git-bug fixes the following issues:\n\nChanges in git-bug:\n\n- CVE-2026-1229: CIRCL had an incorrect calculation in\n  secp384r1 CombinedMult (bsc#1265416, GO-2026-4550):\n  updated github.com/cloudflare/circl to v1.6.3\n- CVE-2026-41506: HTTP authentication credential leak when\n  following redirects during smart-HTTP clone and fetch\n  operations (bsc#1264955, GO-2026-4910):\n  updated github.com/go-git/go-git/v5 to v5.17.1\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
